content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1261.5 - Operator required to report any accident causing injury or damage

State Regulations

The operator of any aircraft involved in any accident
causing personal injury or property damage at an air terminal shall report
promptly of said accident to the manager. Notes
